des: Are you tired of waiting 30 minutes to choose what to eat with your friends? No need to worry, just ask Alexa and her food expert skill. Go through a set of yes or no questions to get just a tad closer to figuring out what do you want to eat. Look forward for increasing food options and funner questions.
